    "body": "## Purpose\r\n\r\nOn H200, we will hit\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n[56/83] Building CUDA object CMakeF...ntization/fp4/nvfp4_quant_entry.cu.o\r\n/home/yewentao256/vllm-source/csrc/quantization/fp4/nvfp4_quant_entry.cu(57): warning #177-D: function \"nvfp4_quant_sm_supported\" was declared but never referenced\r\n  static bool nvfp4_quant_sm_supported() {\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis PR fixes the issue.\r\n",
